---
title: Dukkah-Crusted Pork Schnitzel with Roast Veggie Toss & Herby Yoghurt
description: Eat like an Egyptian by adding dukkah to your dinner! Here, we add the tasty mix of seeds and spices to panko breadcrumbs to create a moreish crust for pork schnitzels. Served with roasted veggies and herby yoghurt, it's definitely a meal to remember.

*Unfortunately, this week's dill was in short supply, so we've replaced it with parsley. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
